elopment and distribution.", "title_alternative": "Linux", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1635654665", "stars": 5756, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 11, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 562222, "username": "hbdh5", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hbdh5", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fb6fdd66157d5ea31318eb6dff87bc3a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fb6fdd66157d5ea31318eb6dff87bc3a?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fb6fdd66157d5ea31318eb6dff87bc3a?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1637221575, "last_modified": 1637221575}, "last_reply_by": "cev2", "last_touched": 1649302466, "title": "有那些好用的靠近上游的 Linux 发行版", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/845331", "created": 1649247579, "deleted": 0, "content": "现在主要用的都是 rhel 或 debian 这些非常稳定但是软件非常老的 distro.\r\n软件包版本太老受不了\r\n蛮久之前用过 ubuntu ，更新经常崩，自此就很久没用过靠近上游的发行版了\r\n主要在家用台式机上使用\r\n\r\n软件包最好相对比较新，但也需要稳定，不要三天两头出问题，系统挂个一两次也挺费时间的", "content_rendered": "<p>现在主要用的都是 rhel 或 debian 这些非常稳定但是软件非常老的 distro.\n软件包版本太老受不了\n蛮久之前用过 ubuntu ，更新经常崩，自此就很久没用过靠近上游的发行版了\n主要在家用台式机上使用</p>\n<p>软件包最好相对比较新，但也需要稳定，不要三天两头出问题，系统挂个一两次也挺费时间的</p>\n", "last_modified": 1649247579, "replies": 66, "id": 845331}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_large.png?m=1648461116", "name": "shanghai", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_normal.png?m=1648461116", "title": "上海", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shanghai", "topics": 2821, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shanghai", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_mini.png?m=1648461116", "stars": 2025, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 18, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 529766, "username": "siwaxinwu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/siwaxinwu", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": n